                            </div>
                        </article>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="g__cell">
                    <a href="lfc.html" class="project__link">
                        <article class="project">
                            <img src="images/proj-thumb-ios-android.jpg" alt="Immersive Media Project showcased on Android and iOS phones" class="project__image">
